---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | CalcSpeed"
  description="CalcSpeed terms of service. Read our terms before using our free online calculators."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-10">Last updated: June 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-8 text-[15px]">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using CalcSpeed at calcspeed.com (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          CalcSpeed provides free, browser-based calculation tools for informational and educational purposes. Our calculators cover areas including mortgage estimation, body mass index, age calculation, salary and tax estimation, daily calorie needs, percentage calculation, time calculation, and grade calculation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>The results produced by CalcSpeed calculators are estimates only and are provided for informational purposes.</strong> They do not constitute financial, legal, medical, tax, or any other professional advice. Specifically:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Mortgage and salary calculations are approximations and may not reflect actual loan terms, lender requirements, or your specific tax situation. Consult a licensed mortgage professional, CPA, or financial advisor before making financial decisions.</li>
          <li>BMI and calorie calculations are health screening estimates based on population-level formulas. They are not medical diagnoses. Consult a qualified healthcare provider for medical advice.</li>
          <li>Grade calculations are tools to help you track your academic progress; they do not guarantee any specific academic outcome.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Accuracy and Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to provide accurate calculations, CalcSpeed makes no warranties or representations regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any calculation results. Tax rates, financial regulations, and other factors change over time. The information provided may not reflect the most current rules or rates.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, CalcSpeed, its owners, and contributors shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages resulting from your use of the Site or reliance on any calculation results.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on CalcSpeed, including text, design, code, and graphics, is owned by CalcSpeed or its content suppliers and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without express written permission.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Site in any manner that could damage, disable, or impair the Site</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site</li>
          <li>Use automated scripts or bots to scrape or excessively access the Site</li>
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Third-Party Advertising</h2>
        <p>
          CalcSpeed displays advertisements through Google AdSense. These ads are served by Google and its partners. We are not responsible for the content of third-party advertisements. Ad presence does not constitute endorsement of any advertised product or service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the United States. Any disputes arising under these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the applicable courts.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these Terms may be directed to us through our <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
